# Salesforce DX project .forceignore file

# Standard files
**/.eslintrc.json
**/.prettierrc
**/jsconfig.json
**/*.md

# LWC configuration files
**/.eslintrc.json
**/package.json
**/jest.config.js

# LWC tests
**/__tests__/**
**/__mocks__/**

# Profiles (use Permission Sets instead)
**/profiles/**

# Local development
.localdevserver/**
.sfdx/**
.sf/**

# Python scripts
**/*.py
**/__pycache__/**

# Logs
*.log
